									Description
					<p style="text-align: justify;">The CCP Series (with &#8220;Ceramkoat&#8221; inner tank) is specially developed for use with NON-POTABLE water. It is a closed-circuit solar water heater that uses standard Flat-Plate panel technology. This unit can be installed on most roof/slabs and is a reliable product that has been designed to minimize the effects of Hard Water and water with High Iron content.<br>Standard Flat-Plate panels use copper risers with machine-welded aluminum fin technology to ensure high efficiency and long-term durability. Supported by the Sacrificial Anode and periodic flushing the effective life of the system is prolonged even beyond standard operational expectations.</p>
<p><img src="http://www.sunbird.lk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/10yearswarranty-300x115.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="115"></p>
<p><strong>10 YEAR WARRANTY</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">This product is covered for all manufacturing defects for installation and use within standard parameters for potable water.</p>
<p><b>1 Year warranty on the Heating Element provided.</b></p>
<p></p>
<p><strong><img src="http://www.sunbird.lk/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/5yearswarranty.jpg" alt="" width="109" height="150">5 YEAR WARRANTY</strong></p>
<p>Specially covered for installation and use for non-potable water (Hard water areas).</p>
<p>(Heating Element provided is not covered for use in bad (Non-potable) water conditions.)</p>
									Features
					<p><strong>System</strong></p><p>â€¢ Suitable for Hard-water/High Iron content<br />â€¢ Suitable for areas with good sunshine<br />â€¢ Operating Pressure: 0 ~ 0.6Mpa (6bar)<br />â€¢ Can be used with a pressure booster pump<br />â€¢ Winner of Presidential Award in Energy<br />â€¢ Delivery pressure equals input pressure (no friction loss)<br />â€¢ Easy-to-do regular maintenance is required<br />â€¢ Stainless Steel anchoring brackets for roof/slab<br /><br /><strong>Hot water Storage Tank</strong></p><p>â€¢ Ceramic-Coated Mild-Steel (3mm)<br />â€¢ Long-lasting aluminum outer body<br />â€¢ Electrical Backup (3kw / 1.5kw)<br />â€¢ Machine-injected high-density Polyurethane foam insulation (50mm)<br />â€¢ UV stabilized fiberglass side covers<br />â€¢ Sacrificial Anode &#8211; User replaceable<br /><br /><strong>Solar Collector</strong></p><p>â€¢ Copper risers for best heat transfer<br />â€¢ Machine-welded blackened Aluminum fins<br />â€¢ Panel Housing &#8211; Aluminum Frame with GI back<br />â€¢ Collector glass (3mm)<br />â€¢ High-quality glassfiber Insulation (25mm)<br />â€¢ Slim Panel design &#8211; only 65mm thick<br /><br /><strong>Safety Components</strong></p><p>â€¢ Anti-Vacuum protection assembly<br />â€¢ Electrical thermostat controller (42Â° ~ 55Â°C)<br />â€¢ Sacrificial Anode <br />â€¢ Auto Air Relief valve<br />â€¢ Non-Return valve at the cold water inlet<br />â€¢ Auto Pressure/Temperature relief valve <br />â€¢ Sediment removal (flushing) valve <br /><br /><strong>Optional components (to purchase separately)</strong></p><p>â€¢ Auto control valve for delivery temperature <br />â€¢ Remote electronic controller (temperature/ pressure) with display<br />â€¢ Premium Flat-plate Panel (Black-chrome plated with 5mm tempered-glass)</p>
